              <p class="leadmargin1">With over two decades of experience across the Automotive, Airline and Engineering IT industries, Kumar Mallampalli currently holds the position of Partner at RheinBrücke IT Consulting. Based out of Chennai, India, he is responsible for delivery, operations and marketing functions of the company.</p>
              <p class="leadmargin1">A Master’s graduate in Structural Engineering from IIT Madras, Kumar launched his career with CAD and structural software development for an Oil and Gas consultancy company. He later moved to NIIT Technologies and shifted base to London, for an 8 year stint with British Airways as the Delivery Manager for UK and India.</p>
              <p class="leadmargin1">Kumar’s varied experience includes his role as the Automotive Global Delivery Head at Satyam Computers, delivering a range of services across geographies on multi-year engagements. He also managed customers, alliances, pre-sales, development, production support, IT service management, maintenance, testing as well as infrastructure and consultancy projects. He had complete ownership of delivery and service level agreements for a thousand member team across Americas, Europe, APAC and India.</p>
              <p class="leadmargin1">Prior to joining RheinBrücke, Kumar Mallampalli was the Head of Emerging Technologies, ERP and IT Services at Defiance Technologies for five years. He also had P&L ownership for SAP, EPICOR, MS Dynamics, Mobility, Social Media Analytics & Digital Marketing, Enterprise Collaboration, Telematics, Web and Custom Development to global customers on the Microsoft as well as Open Source platforms.</p>
              <p class="leadmargin1">At RheinBrücke, Kumar is responsible for solutions, competencies and alliances in the Global Delivery Model, Operations as well as developing and managing marketing worldwide.</p>     
